:user ri:account-id=\"712020:bd6be9b3-2ff0-412b-8fb1-57e9e188f6cf\" ri:local-id=\"f25ddf58-7303-46cb-ba14-c6bbff926928\" /></ac:link> y <ac:link><ri:user ri:account-id=\"632e0ea3409249995ee8d951\" ri:local-id=\"6f95cf25-f27f-4378-b1f1-1e8126dbc04f\" /></ac:link> .</p><p local-id=\"44ad7740-0aa1-44c7-9667-6dcc96e20c62\">Las horas estimadas son: <strong>128 ~ 8 d&iacute;as por desarrollador.</strong></p><p local-id=\"975087fe-de7b-4822-9fb2-664e579ec031\">Fecha de Inicio: <strong>Jueves</strong> <time datetime=\"2025-11-27\" local-id=\"2b44018e-e3f5-4959-8cf8-f57773de19b2\" /></p><p local-id=\"6233661e-4d36-471c-a2e1-677b40e0b712\">Fecha de Entrega:  <time datetime=\"2024-12-05\" local-id=\"ee0f9082-94c7-4b3e-9151-d66a2a95cc2d\" /> </p></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"d127e8c3-3fed-4af2-bc1b-c09b7117def2\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 539.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 221.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr ac:local-id=\"74f31eb1-b762-4a67-b080-b4cbb4186a30\"><th ac:local-id=\"df9cd2aa-2b76-45fb-85d2-6947ec95140f\"><p local-id=\"f9b38245-79e6-4e54-8acc-dd93856203dd\"><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th ac:local-id=\"7b78a5c1-515a-4bb9-a338-b7f105a2b415\"><p local-id=\"16307eb6-093a-4b2e-96bf-9d89c1552519\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"e8976368-e06b-4950-89ee-c0d3a6120287\"><td ac:local-id=\"ca2f74f5-23fe-4f92-900d-e93278468efd\"><p local-id=\"4586e781-113c-45fb-89ba-516a09f4bad7\">An&aacute;lisis del requerimiento (TPago y VPos)</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"fb8050ea-23c2-46cc-bd35-677d0d647bce\"><p local-id=\"d8f33464-d27e-46a7-b9cd-ba825c568765\">24hs (12hs Julian + 12hs Gaston)</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"90798881-f968-4238-a432-5e6d7c75f537\"><td ac:local-id=\"d0776cfd-db3f-4a67-85ad-eb8e04e66621\"><p local-id=\"bffc36a9-6bd6-413b-b3a2-68c2ad2ce07b\">Desarrollo TPago</p></td><td ac:local-id=\"15b747c9-bf6b-4b7f-a0c9-b73a0f