cal-id=\"50da3bce-5a61-4a23-a221-1de8192ef166\"><p local-id=\"320e407b-d489-44f5-9e66-5668c06e6b92\">Pruebas iniciales en STG</p></li></ul></td><td ac:local-id=\"5e7e49a8-589b-4b28-8452-30c01feb530d\"><p local-id=\"cfa91f7d-5bb3-4d99-924c-b5aa3c4afe15\">8h</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"13ae532d-ac52-4e3b-ac65-b5c4bdfbb074\"><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\" ac:local-id=\"767334d5-b9ff-4c60-8cc7-5f3bf2dd192f\"><p local-id=\"1bf16df0-ee2b-4064-9efc-ee6b1ab96e3c\"><strong>Total Desarrollo</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\" ac:local-id=\"e62746de-9b6a-40dd-9aca-4c0f87660c20\"><p local-id=\"3addfe52-0e7e-4549-9c23-9a756d6478a9\" style=\"text-align: center;\">112</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"f8fd93fc-f23f-41b1-8089-ca5adb038b92\"><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\" ac:local-id=\"8173804a-b9dd-4861-a411-a585b297f6ca\"><p local-id=\"da47c819-997c-4c7b-a55c-d58fc1dfc638\"><strong>Total Gesti&oacute;n 15% (para facturaci&oacute;n, no afecta el desarrollo)</strong></p><p local-id=\"e4823b1d-3a12-49b8-8ca7-2535121aa2ed\"><em>Incluye reuniones de estimaci&oacute;n, planificaci&oacute;n, t&eacute;cnicas y de seguimiento.</em></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\" ac:local-id=\"72a019e8-b4bc-47e5-a6ea-49ad66efbf1b\"><p local-id=\"d038ea6c-e0fa-4605-8325-9184c5acf21a\" style=\"text-align: center;\">16</p></td></tr><tr ac:local-id=\"a2d0ab55-fcaa-4439-9e79-cdfd8ed9c930\"><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\" ac:local-id=\"30e31211-d4f9-4c1c-85d2-f093e19f03d2\"><p local-id=\"e42dde19-9dcd-46fa-b2a4-f3e338cc962b\"><strong>Total Desarrollo + Gesti&oacute;n</strong></p></td><td data-highlight-colour=\"#eae6ff\" ac:local-id=\"0adbb7d6-414c-44f8-afe6-55ec5cb2dbb8\"><p local-id=\"18cff64e-8dc7-445c-9406-52f65e3490f7\" style=\"text-align: center;\">128</p></td></tr></tbody></table>","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/4407132161"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_v